text: Riesbach is a district in the city of Zürich in Switzerland. It is District number 8. ==History== The district has these quarters: Seefeld, Mühlebach and Weinegg. Until 1893 it was a municipality on its own. Then it was added to Zürich. ==Other websites== Category:Former municipalities of Zürich Category:Quarters of Zürich Category:Switzerland stubs
